{"tid":1185043,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"幣少以3100萬美金買左同巴菲特午餐","createTime":"2019-06-04T04:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T06:43:10.000Z","uid":78492,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa065c09f60676cd594e5af57e469617a6b07bc","tid":1185043,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"2019年巴菲特慈善午餐拍賣贏家身份揭曉！中國人、來自「幣圈」、90後&mdash;&mdash;波場TRON創始人孫宇晨。<br />\n<br />\n孫宇晨通過推特正式發佈了這一消息：「我正式宣佈，我贏得了創下紀錄的20屆巴菲特慈善午餐拍賣。我還會邀請區塊鏈行業的領軍者們一起會見這位投資泰斗。我希望這會讓每一個人都受益。」<br />\n<br />\n消息下方，孫宇晨還發布了一張自己的宣傳照，左側是滿臉笑容的巴菲特，右側則寫有「以456.7888萬美元贏得巴菲特慈善午餐拍賣」的字樣。 <br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，巴菲特一直對比特幣持厭惡、懷疑態度，所以消息傳出後，大家第一反應是，這飯要怎麼吃？<br />\n<br />\n據新浪財經最新報道，當巴菲特被問及他如何評論中國加密貨幣企業家中標慈善午餐一事時，他朗聲大笑，並且表示，期待着這次午餐的到來。"},{"pid":"5128e100d152c2e222dd1a92e2ef826f5f5aa115","tid":1185043,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"巴菲特:<br />\n<br />\nwhy you so on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7586517cd56870ff2499c98e28ab680c6662aedc","tid":1185043,"uid":254425,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:57:30.000Z","msg":"幣少唔等於justin sun <br />\n唔識唔好9up<br />\ntron贏fcc 10條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8d2a09ed2f6241ad78c3830e26609163da7b7f","tid":1185043,"uid":207710,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"美紙港紙唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8ffb4f51a7637e328dd407ae2ffe863ec1d3e0","tid":1185043,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"Cringe <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9abd0c741186b4ad20f49090daa92f3e77ec08","tid":1185043,"uid":78492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7586517cd56870ff2499c98e28ab680c6662aedc","tid":1185043,"uid":254425,"like":9,"dislike":